    <p id="p_kdh_dgk_54b">The <b>Oxygen AI Positron Enterprise</b> add-on provides advanced support for technical documentation writers throughout their content creation process by allowing you to configure a company-specific AI service. <b id="b_mqx_ftk_21c">OpenAI</b>, <b id="b_jkd_gtk_21c">Microsoft Azure OpenAI</b>, <b>Anthropic Claude</b>, <b>Google Gemini</b>, and <b>xAI Grok</b> are provided as default configuration options, but you can also connect to Google's <b>Vertex AI Service</b> by installing the <xref href="ai-positron-vertex-ai-connector.dita"/> or you can configure a custom service by installing the <xref href="ai-positron-custom-connector.dita"/>, </p>
    <p>Installation, features, and customization:<ul>
        <li><xref href="ai_positron_enterprise-installation.dita"/></li>
        <li><xref href="ai_positron_functionality_features.dita"/></li>
        <li><xref href="ai_positron_enterprise-preferences.dita"/></li>
        <li><xref href="ai_positron_enterprise-config-file.dita"/></li>
        <li><xref href="creating_custom_ai_actions.dita"/></li>
        <li><xref href="ai_positron_enterprise-extending.dita"/></li>
      </ul></p>
    <section id="section_x2n_vhh_vrb">
      <title>Demos (Videos, Webinars)</title>
      <p id="p_orm_dgk_54b">To watch a demonstration of the AI Positron add-on, along with various uses cases for using the tool, see the following recorded webinars: <ul id="ul_tf1_w1l_f2c">
          <li id="li_uf1_w1l_f2c"><xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/events/2023/webinar_ai_as_a_tool_for_technical_content_creation.html" format="html" scope="external">AI as a Tool for Technical Content Creation</xref></li>
          <li id="li_z25_w1l_f2c"><xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/events/2024/webinar_ai_positron_your_helper_in_all_stages_of_content_creation.html" format="html" scope="external">Oxygen AI Positron: Your Helper in All Stages of Content Creation</xref></li>
          <li id="li_ag1_y1l_f2c"><xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/events/2023/webinar_transforming_technical_content_creation_through_ai_powered_writing.html" format="html" scope="external">Oxygen AI Positron: Transforming Technical Content Creation through AI-Powered Writing</xref></li>
        </ul></p>
      <p id="p_yxx_byf_tfc">See ways to use AI development tools (e.g. from XSLT stylesheets and Schematron schemas) in the following recorded webinars:<ul id="ul_bj1_dbl_f2c">
